      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BALINGUP BOY (5) has been racing without luck. Showed good improvement second-up when he raced three wide but was beaten less than 5m at Gloucester Park. Peaking now and goes well at this circuit and distance with a win and two placings from four attempts. I SEE FIRE (4) did a good job to come from a 20m handicap and finish second last start, beaten a head at Northam. Can go one better without surprising. HONOUR THE EAGLE (2) hasn't been too far off the placegetters in two outings since a second at this venue. Draws for a good showing. ISLAND TEE REX (7) draws wide but has some claims off a win from the second line two back at Narrogin.",
